A multiple regression model to show the above effects¶

  • PMd Lat Index ~ treatment + task + treatment x task + ID

  • Compared to the control group, the CIMT group shows greater activation of the ipsilesional PMd during the precision, but not the power task, with the affected limb.

  • Check out this article by Kantak for a possible explanation: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4886541/
